SECTION 2 — REDESIGN: Make forms compact and chat-native
==============================================================================
CURRENT PROBLEM: Forms are large (7-8 fields, textarea, full-width) and feel 
like a web form dropped into chat. They should feel like part of the conversation.

DESIGN PRINCIPLES:
- Max width: 380px (mobile-card feel, not full-width)
- Compact padding: 12px internal
- Label font: 11px, uppercase, tracking-wide, muted color
- Input height: 32px (not 40px+)
- Font size in inputs: 13px
- Minimal borders — use subtle backgrounds instead of heavy borders
- Submit/Cancel inline side-by-side at the bottom
- No heavy card shadow — just a thin border
- Feels like a Slack /slash command form, not an admin panel form

IMPLEMENT IN src/components/FormRenderer.jsx:

A. WRAPPER: Change the outer container from full-width to:
   className="w-full max-w-[380px] rounded-xl border border-slate-200 
   dark:border-slate-700 bg-white dark:bg-slate-800/60 p-3 my-1"

B. TITLE: Make it small and inline:
   className="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-slate-500 
   dark:text-slate-400 mb-2.5 pb-2 border-b border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700"

C. DESCRIPTION (if present): 
   className="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-2 -mt-1"

D. FIELDS LAYOUT: Change from 2-column grid to single column, compact spacing:
   className="flex flex-col gap-2"

   For each field:
   - Label: className="block text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide 
     text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-0.5"
   - Text/number input: className="w-full px-2.5 py-1.5 text-[13px] rounded-lg 
     border bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-700/50 border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-600 
     text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 outline-none focus:border-blue-500 
     focus:ring-1 focus:ring-blue-500/20 transition-colors"
   - Textarea: same as above but rows={3} — NOT rows={5} or more
   - Select: same as text input with appearance-none
   - Error text: "mt-0.5 text-[11px] text-red-400 flex items-center gap-1"

E. TABLE/ARRAY FIELDS (if form has rows): Keep rows compact — 
   32px row height, 11px fonts, minimal padding.

F. FOOTER BUTTONS: Side-by-side, right-aligned:
   <div className="flex justify-end gap-2 mt-3 pt-2.5 
   border-t border-slate-100 dark:border-slate-700">
     <button Cancel className="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-medium text-slate-500 
       dark:text-slate-400 hover:text-slate-700 dark:hover:text-slate-200 
       transition-colors">
       {cancelLabel}
     </button>
     <button Submit className="px-4 py-1.5 text-xs font-semibold rounded-lg 
       bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white transition-colors 
       disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed shadow-sm">
       {submitLabel}
     </button>
   </div>

G. SUBMITTED STATE: When form is submitted successfully, replace form with 
   a compact inline chip:
   <div className="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg 
   bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/20 text-emerald-400 text-xs font-medium">
     <CheckCircle2 size={12} />
     <span>{formSpec.title} submitted</span>
   </div>

H. CANCELLED STATE: When cancelled, replace with:
   <div className="text-xs text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 italic">
     Form cancelled.
   </div>

